metadata.description: LAUNCH POINT Last year, Liesel Van Helsing was attacked by an evil from her father's past? but she survived, and has moved on with her life. Besides becoming the name that vampires in the tri-state area fear, she's also found love - in, admittedly, the strangest places. However, when old friends come calling on her for help, she will find herself pulled into a final conflict with the deadliest vampire of all time?
metadata.name: Van Helsing vs. Dracula
